EducationData.name: University of Tennessee
EducationData.description: Pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science with a minor in machine learning. I am expected to graduate in May 2027. I am currently a member of the Chancellor's Honors Program, Cook Grand Honors Program, and Dean's List. During my time at UT, I have explored a variety of reserach labs ranging to micro electronics to computational chemistry. I have served as a Resident Assistant and as the events director for the Society of Asian Scientists and Engineers.
